<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>UBarbershop – About</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

    <link href="../public/css/about.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="../public/css/header_footer.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>

<body>

    {% include "utils/header.html.twig" %}
    
    <!-- Main -->
    <main class="about-page">

        <h1 data-i18n="about.title">About This Business</h1>

        <div class="about-card">

            <h2 data-i18n="about.subtitle">
                A Young Woman’s First Business Journey
            </h2>

            <p data-i18n="about.p1">
                UBarbershop was created as the first business venture of a young woman
                driven by passion, determination, and a desire to build something
                meaningful. Opening this barbershop represents an important milestone
                and the beginning of an exciting entrepreneurial journey.
            </p>

            <p data-i18n="about.p2">
                The goal of UBarbershop is to provide a welcoming, professional space
                where clients feel confident, comfortable, and valued. Every detail —
                from the atmosphere to the services offered — has been carefully
                considered to deliver quality and consistency, including the
                complimentary refreshments offered to all clients during their visit.
            </p>

            <p data-i18n="about.p3">
                This business is more than just a barbershop; it is a reflection of hard
                work, perseverance, and the courage it takes to turn a vision into
                reality. It stands as proof that with dedication and ambition, a first
                business can become something truly special.
            </p>

            <p class="thanks" data-i18n="about.thanks">
                Thank you for supporting a local business and being part of this journey!
            </p>

        </div>

    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    {% include 'utils/footer.html.twig' %}

    <!-- Scripts -->
    <script src="../js/headerAuth.js" type="module"></script>
    <script src="../js/lang.js"></script>
    <script src="../js/hamburgerMenu.js"></script>
    <script src="../js/activeNav.js"></script>

</body>
</html>